---
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split split--reverse">
      <div>
        <img src="/images/fogueira.webp" alt="Bonfire at Maceda Surf Camp" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Surfing, Nature and Doing Life Properly</h2>
        <p>Since 2011, we've been doing the same simple thing well: creating a place people genuinely want to come back to.</p>
        <p>Here's what you do get:</p>
        <ul class="list-check">
          <li>A welcoming place that feels like a little surf family</li>
          <li>Long, uncrowded beaches where you can surf alone</li>
          <li>Supportive people who meet you where you're at</li>
          <li>Shared meals, fires, music and easy convos</li>
          <li>A peaceful, nature-first setting to help you switch off</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="dont-get">And what you don't get:</p>
        <ul class="list-x">
          <li>Hardcore partying</li>
          <li>Pressure to be outgoing</li>
          <li>Packed schedules</li>
          <li>Competitive vibes</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#book" class="btn">Book Now!</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .list-check, .list-x {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .list-check li, .list-x li {
    padding: 0.25rem 0 0.25rem 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .list-check li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .list-x li::before {
    content: '✕';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .dont-get {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>
